                        <li style="font-size: x-large;">The service can also be used to provide a sophisticated network monitoring solution that allows network administrators, webmasters, and Internet service providers to monitor any networked device on the Internet, and receive alerts immediately via e-mail, or third-party software when a connection fails.</li><br>
